column5: I was looking through the various enteries in the OFC 2008 Tourney Entries fourm and i must say you all caught lot's of big fish so far this year. Congradulations to all who managed to get their pictures up. I hope were doing another tournament next year!  WTG everyone
It's not over yet.... 30 days left to boost your teams score ! ...14 of them for Muskie.
